      "value": "Sacrifice HP for massive damage."
    },
    "description": "<blockquote><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>Requirements: </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">you must have mastered the </span><strong>Darkblade </strong><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Class.</span> </p></blockquote><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">When you hit a creature with an attack, if that attack </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>only </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">targeted that creature and you have a </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>Bond </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">towards them, you may choose to spend half of your current Hit Points, rounded down. If you do, the attack deals extra damage equal to </span><span class=\"fontstyle3\"><strong>【</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>10 multiplied by the strength of your Bond towards the target</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle3\"><strong>】</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">.</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">You may use this Skill only on your turn during a conflict, and </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>only once per turn</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">.</span> </p><hr /><p><strong>@DMG[10 untyped] @DMG[20 untyped] @DMG[30 untyped]</strong></p>",
